Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Gives the Tanker a chance of increasing their resistance by a small amount for 20 seconds, this effect stacks up to 3 times, and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This effect will trigger roughly 5 times per minute.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Tankers and may be slotted into any Tanker damage power.
DisplayName: Attuned Might of the Tanker F
